<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Payment Deadline Passed</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #ef4444;">⚠️ Payment Deadline Passed</h1>
  
  <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
  
  <p>Unfortunately, the payment deadline for your winning bid has passed.</p>
  
  <div style="background: #fee2e2; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p><strong>Product:</strong> {{productName}}</p>
    <p><strong>Your Winning Bid:</strong> Rp {{winningBid}}</p>
  </div>
  
  <p>This auction will be re-listed and offered to other bidders.</p>
  
  <p>If you experienced technical issues, please contact support at support@tcgstore.com</p>
  
  <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">© {{year}} TCG Store. All rights reserved.</p>
</body>
</html>